  <footer>
    This tool queries the NHS Business Services Authority
    <em>English Prescribing Dataset (EPD) with SNOMED Code</em> via the public CKAN Data API.
    Data © NHSBSA, licensed under the Open Government Licence.  [oai_citation:2‡opendata.nhsbsa.net](https://opendata.nhsbsa.net/dataset/english-prescribing-dataset-epd-with-snomed-code)
